{"Id":741455,"Title":"漂母祠","Dynasty":"清","Author":"李振钧","Context":"儒坑兵销长城筑。天下苦秦几上肉。纷纷攘臂争一呼。淮阴壮士甘穷途。布衣仗剑来都市。亭长晨炊少年訾。谁知慷慨哀王孙，不在须眉在女子。斩蛇道中老妪哀。垂钓城下漂母来。君臣遭遇皆奇绝，一知气数一怜才。䌟絖终日依淮浦。壶飧解劳风尘苦。物色已居滕公先，意气终羞绛灌伍。一饭殷勤讵望酬。千秋庙貌临清流。我来吊古重惆怅，双双翠羽鸣啾啾。君不见鸟尽弓藏良将死。皓首功名同白起。长乐受缚谁为怜。吕后何如漂母贤。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"0a44b1f691d02fafa35698dadc2d5466","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5510945,"Sentence":"谁知慷慨哀王孙，不在须眉在女子。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shéi zhī kāng kǎi āi wáng sūn ，bú zài xū méi zài nǚ zi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510944,"Sentence":"亭长晨炊少年訾。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tǐng cháng chén chuī shǎo nián zī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510939,"Sentence":"儒坑兵销长城筑。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"rú kēng bīng xiāo cháng chéng zhú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510940,"Sentence":"天下苦秦几上肉。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tiān xià kǔ qǐn jī shǎng ròu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510941,"Sentence":"纷纷攘臂争一呼。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fēn fēn rǎng 臂zhēng yī hū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510942,"Sentence":"淮阴壮士甘穷途。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huái yīn zhuàng shì gān qióng tú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510943,"Sentence":"布衣仗剑来都市。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bù yī zhàng jiàn lái dōu shì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510946,"Sentence":"斩蛇道中老妪哀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhǎn shé dāo zhōng lǎo yǔ āi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5510947,"Sentence":"垂钓城下漂母来。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chuǐ diào chéng xià piāo mǔ lái ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"